metadata.name: CoinyLabs Intern (sketch)
metadata.description:
One sunny day, a young lady arrived at Coinylabs, an NFT research lab located on a mysterious island. She had always been fascinated by the world of cryptocurrency, and had heard great things about Coinylabs.

As she walked through the shiny front doors, she was greeted by a friendly receptionist who directed her to the main research area, walking by rows of holographic screens and chalkboards filled with complex equations and diagrams. She was filled with excitement and wonder.

Finally, she arrived at the main lab where a group of scientific potatoes were hard at work. To her surprise, they immediately hired her as an intern!
